1
00:00:04,971 --> 00:00:06,787
Really, that’s what we’re looking for. 

2
00:00:06,787 --> 00:00:11,032
We’re looking for that person
who, upon connecting with,

3
00:00:11,032 --> 00:00:13,810
we realise,
“This is my eternal connection. 

4
00:00:13,810 --> 00:00:16,121
I have always and only been
in love with this person.”

5
00:00:16,198 --> 00:00:19,907
[The Ideal Person]

6
00:00:20,613 --> 00:00:23,684
But we’re thinking
it’s someone in this world,

7
00:00:23,684 --> 00:00:27,080
when actually,
it’s the Absolute Person.

8
00:00:27,080 --> 00:00:29,522
And only the Absolute Person
is capable

9
00:00:29,522 --> 00:00:34,483
of reciprocating
that type of connection,

10
00:00:34,567 --> 00:00:41,234
amazingly, astonishingly, 
with everyone.

11
00:00:41,653 --> 00:00:47,497
That One can reciprocate
every atom of the heart’s hankering,

12
00:00:47,497 --> 00:00:54,199
of every living being,
simultaneously.

13
00:00:54,937 --> 00:00:57,340
That’s the Absolute,

14
00:00:57,340 --> 00:01:02,138
and the Absolute cannot be
anything less than that;

15
00:01:03,138 --> 00:01:07,387
it’s the Absolute Personality of Godhead.

16
00:01:07,834 --> 00:01:13,781
And we, through ideal search criteria,
indirectly, are searching.

17
00:01:13,781 --> 00:01:18,850
It’s an acknowledgement that
we’re searching for the Absolute,

18
00:01:19,291 --> 00:01:22,758
the Ultimate Beautiful Person,

19
00:01:22,789 --> 00:01:26,929
the Ultimate Loving Person.

20
00:01:28,375 --> 00:01:30,033
The person who’s capable …

21
00:01:30,033 --> 00:01:34,460
“Prati anga lagi kande, prati anga mora”
(Jnana Dasa),

22
00:01:34,460 --> 00:01:40,614
every atom of our soul is
crying out for its correspondent,

23
00:01:40,614 --> 00:01:42,255
and that can only be found

24
00:01:42,255 --> 00:01:45,100
in the Absolute Personality of Godhead.

